transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan ji. Haan ji Deepak ji kaise hain aap?
Customer: Bas theek hai ji aap batao.
Executive: Badhiya sir badhiya. Ye sir kal aapka discussion hua tha Payal Goyal aapke account mein unke sath IndiaMART pe. Video meeting vgera bhi hui thi na?
Customer: Haan hui thi.
Executive: Ji ji ji. To sir aapne jaise call ka ek feedback jata hai aapko. Uspe aapne wo not satisfied mark kiya tha matlab janna chah raha tha.
Customer: Kya?
Executive: Discussion aapne kal Payal Goyal aapke account mein unke sath baat hui thi aapki?
Customer: Haan hui thi.
Executive: Ji bilkul video meeting hui thi sir aapke sath.
Customer: [unintelligible]
